; Coverage for history.cc price inversion in find_price
; When the price's commodity matches the source, the price must be inverted
; P $ EUR means 1$ = 0.91 EUR, so 1 EUR = 1/0.91 $

P 2024/01/01 $ 0.91 EUR

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Travel    500 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --market --exchange '$' --now 2024/02/01 Expenses
                $549  Expenses:Travel
end test
